50|$|The 13th MEU’s special {{operations}} capabilities (SOC) were used extensively on its deployment during Operation Desert Shield and Operation Desert Storm. Beginning a routine deployment 20 June 1990, the MEU was diverted to Southwest Asia in August. The first amphibious force {{to arrive in}} the theater of operations, personnel conducted the first Marine offensive <b>actions</b> <b>against</b> <b>Iraq.</b> In October, elements boarded two Iraqi tankers that refused to obey United Nations sanctions.|$|R
